回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T02:06:43.000Z","msg":"佢地加入，777管治威信冇哂，可以換人"},{"pid":"7fa97a62dbc5f3888cd0d141de8dc184cb275755","tid":1170261,"uid":198278,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T02:22:00.000Z","msg":"睇完上邊咁多條片，令我諗返少少歷史<br />\n<br />\n50年代的印尼獨立戰爭<br />\n80年代的羅馬尼亞內戰<br />\n90年代至今的納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫戰爭<br />\n都喺由示威變成真正行動<br />\n<br />\n我覺得我哋最需要嘅喺信念<br />\n示威雖然唔重要<br />\n但絕對喺重要一步<br />\n就喺為咗堅持我哋嘅信念<br />\n我哋先要企出嚟發聲<br />\n對當權者嗆聲"},{"pid":"bb7b50bf02d96bc941da1c6be329208ce9ac7d55","tid":1170261,"uid":73804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T02:22:14.000Z","msg":"睇呢d片又真係覺得雨革同魚革係幼稚園level"},{"pid":"0a9967b93f4511b5639ddca20278aece518b9486","tid":1170261,"uid":254594,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T02:26:41.000Z","msg":"「嚴酷的刑罰與法治不相容，不應該用極端手段，而應以溫和的方法。如果所有刑罰的嚴厲程度相同，那麼人們將傾向於犯大罪而非小罪。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當政府打壓聲音力量越大<br />\n人們犯小事卻換來不成比例的刑罰 只會令犯事者更傾向放下戒心 反正結果都是一樣<br />\n所以示威者都一樣係潘朵拉的盒子 當權者要警剔下唔好玩火"},{"pid":"fc32b44ffece98ef3e80d8b8a12361a2c6afc508","tid":1170261,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T02:34:04.000Z","msg":"點都好,安全至上"},{"pid":"ba61e9c2d85f806a68c0fd9e614e87a06a7c839a","tid":1170261,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T04:20:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"145b29feed71f7a2ad2590583d4ac392034307b6","tid":1170261,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bcdaeb8e4134b69abd2a9bf82c04fcd6ac6ce96","tid":1170261,"uid":27151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:27:24.000Z","msg":"國際標準嘅示威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d720de9787352f5f04bb127f91b181e794d7bef4","tid":1170261,"uid":35014,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score